# Protocol 28 — Authority classification (bridge-os)

| Class | Examples in this repo |
| ----- | --------------------- |
| **S** | Human legal sign-off, user **stop**, do not commit/push |
| **A** | XR-401 attestations, `trust:attest:*:write`, protocols log append, `gh` coordination posts when authorized |
| **R** | `verify:operational`, `agent:next-work`, coordination hygiene |

Trust attestation runners are **Class A** after preceremony gates — execute and write evidence to protocols.

**Spec:** https://github.com/gtcx-ecosystem/gtcx-docs/blob/main/docs/governance/protocols/28-agent-authority-classification/protocol.md
